description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2:

Florida, UK evidence shows masks aren't needed in schools. C&B take calls from parents on vaccine mandate for kids. Author and analyst Gordon Chang on the China threat. Doocy hits Psaki on DOJ targeting parents at school boards.
